HEADWORD: pacifism
<hw>pacifism</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the doctrine that all violence is
unjustifiable.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> passivism.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The belief that all international disputes can be
settled by arbitration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>pacifist</ent>⟦br⟧
